mapper.select: SELECT sch_name, academic_year as stuclayear, rounds as stuSeq, grade as stuClalevel, clazz_name as stuClassname, stu_name, stu_birth, stu_sex, stu_phone, cid FROM nur_stuinfo stu LEFT JOIN nur_school sch ON stu.schid = sch.sch_id where stu_isjz = '2' and sch_id = #{schId} and year= #{year} and grade = #{grade} and round = #{round} and clazz_name = #{className}

select ns.*, nc.SCH_STATIONNAME stuStationname, nc.SCH_NAME schname from nur_stuinfo ns left join nur_school nc on ns.SCHID=nc.SCH_ID where ns.stu_no=#{stuNo} and ns.schId=#{schId} order by STU_UPDATETIME desc limit 1

select ns.*, nc.SCH_STATIONNAME stuStationname, nc.SCH_NAME schname from nur_stuinfo ns left join nur_school nc on ns.SCHID=nc.SCH_ID where ns.cid=#{cid} and ns.schId=#{schId} order by STU_UPDATETIME desc LIMIT 1
